title: #53 - Top Of The Week With Ian Hecox
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast we're joined by Ian Hecox of Smosh for another round of Top Of The Week! Together we discuss Papa John's fall from grace, Barbara Streisand cloning her dog, and the threat of thermonuclear annihilation! Ian Hecox is the co-creator of the sketch comedy YouTube channel Smosh.
